// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1566 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: f711b5fe-d520-5481-9c4f-3961fca5a2f5

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:25.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:26.04*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
